1
00:01:09,240 --> 00:01:10,680
Mianxian hu!

2
00:01:14,800 --> 00:01:17,060
Sir, would you like a bowl of mianxian hu?

3
00:01:17,440 --> 00:01:18,039
Come here.

4
00:01:18,080 --> 00:01:19,680
Reactionary Lin Zhongzheng

5
00:01:19,720 --> 00:01:20,560
will be executed in three days.

6
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:21,289
Come and see.

7
00:01:21,520 --> 00:01:23,200
Let this be a warning to you all.

8
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:23,730
Wangshu.

9
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:25,680
Don't be impulsive.

10
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:26,200
Their spies are

11
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:27,200
everywhere here.

12
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:29,760
Follow me.

13
00:01:44,600 --> 00:01:45,120
Boss.

14
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,039
One liang of chopped green onion.

15
00:01:47,039 --> 00:01:48,570
How much flavor does it add?

16
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:49,700
One spoon of chili.

17
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:51,420
Adds five points of umami.

18
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:52,920
Why are you back?

19
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:55,039
President Qin was afraid

20
00:01:55,039 --> 00:01:55,960
you'd come back on impulse

21
00:01:55,960 --> 00:01:57,840
and be discovered by the Japanese.

22
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:59,320
My father is going to be executed.

23
00:01:59,320 --> 00:02:00,780
How could we not come back?

24
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:03,760
Where are President Qin and the others now?

25
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:05,200
They are all at the chamber of commerce,

26
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,320
still trying to find a way.

27
00:02:06,320 --> 00:02:07,480
Go this way.

28
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:08,400
Be careful.

29
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,289
Okay, thank you.

30
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:12,120
Let's go.

31
00:02:12,440 --> 00:02:13,640
Mianxianhu!

32
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:17,760
Who told you three to come back?

33
00:02:17,760 --> 00:02:19,800
Aren't you just walking right into a trap?

34
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:21,860
Isn't there enough trouble already?

35
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:23,360
You...

36
00:02:25,079 --> 00:02:25,560
Mr. Qin.

37
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,040
My dad was falsely accused and imprisoned.

38
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:27,720
As his children,

39
00:02:27,720 --> 00:02:29,180
how can we just sit around?

40
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,040
Calm down.

41
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,480
Hurry up and tell us

42
00:02:31,480 --> 00:02:33,140
about the current situation.

43
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:37,490
Luo Wang didn't catch Jiadong.

44
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,600
The crimes of the Japanese tea factory

45
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:40,120
were published in the newspapers again.

46
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:41,160
Yamada was furious

47
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:42,560
and almost shot Luo Wang.

48
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:45,060
To make amends,

49
00:02:45,079 --> 00:02:46,280
he knelt for several days.

50
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,280
Finally, he came up with

51
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:47,960
a malicious plan

52
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,490
to make up for his mistakes.

53
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:50,720
That is to frame Old Lin,

54
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:52,650
saying he opposes the government.

55
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:53,380
The purpose

56
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:55,260
is to force Jiadong to show up.

57
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:56,040
Exactly.

58
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:57,560
Last night,

59
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,440
the Japanese burned down

60
00:02:58,440 --> 00:03:00,040
three of their own warehouses.

61
00:03:00,040 --> 00:03:01,120
Then they turned around and framed

62
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:03,080
our Chinese Chamber of Commerce for it.

63
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:05,520
The Chamber of Commerce is in grave danger now.

64
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:06,880
The power of the Japanese

65
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:08,680
is growing stronger and stronger.

66
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,920
The greedy Songkan

67
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,360
and Malayan authorities

68
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,960
are completely unreliable.

69
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:13,960
We can't

70
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:15,440
think of any way right now

71
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:17,120
to save Boss Lin.

72
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:20,920
I don't care anymore.

73
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:22,640
I'll just hijack the prisoner tonight.

74
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:23,040
You!

75
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:24,200
Otherwise, in three days,

76
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:25,400
Dad will be executed.

77
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:26,079
Nonsense!

78
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:27,250
Sit down.

79
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:29,410
Wangshu, sit down quickly.

80
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,440
Since Luowang and Yamada's goal

81
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:33,440
is to lure us back,

82
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:34,560
whether it's the prison cell

83
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,440
holding Dad

84
00:03:35,640 --> 00:03:36,720
or the square,

85
00:03:36,880 --> 00:03:37,680
they are all closely monitored

86
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:38,610
by their people.

87
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:39,960
We can't act rashly.

88
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,480
Are we just going to watch Dad

89
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:43,200
die?

90
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,800
I'll go ask around for news.

91
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,720
Don't go.

92
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,780
You are all so foolish.

93
00:03:52,480 --> 00:03:54,079
Old Zhao and I will go.

94
00:03:55,040 --> 00:03:55,560
Mr. Qin.

95
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:56,120
Listen.

96
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:57,490
Without my word,

97
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,160
don't leave here.

98
00:04:00,880 --> 00:04:01,520
Mr. Qin.

99
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:10,700
President Yamada.

100
00:04:11,320 --> 00:04:12,450
Please don't worry.

101
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:15,360
Once Chen Jiadong and the others get the news,

102
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:17,279
they will definitely rush back to Malaya.

103
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:18,920
We will lay an ambush in advance.

104
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:19,560
Then we can catch them

105
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,220
all at once.

106
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:21,079
Maybe they

107
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,170
have already...

108
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,760
At this point,

109
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:25,760
do you think

110
00:04:26,520 --> 00:04:28,360
just killing these few Chinese

111
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:31,000
can make up for my losses?

112
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,420
President Yamada.

113
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,730
Then what is your real purpose?

114
00:05:02,080 --> 00:05:02,800
This is...

115
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:05,640
Our Great Japanese Empire's

116
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:07,760
grand goal is to

117
00:05:08,960 --> 00:05:10,620
conquer all of Southeast Asia

118
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:14,410
and establish the Greater East Asia Co-Prosperity Sphere.

119
00:05:14,640 --> 00:05:15,880
A few mere Chinese

120
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,400
mean nothing to me.

121
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:20,920
Once we become

122
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,260
the masters of Malaya,

123
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:25,560
they will just be

124
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:28,160
meat waiting to be slaughtered.

125
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:29,960
In that case,

126
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:31,760
could you tell me

127
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:34,580
why you went to such great lengths

128
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,570
to bring Chen Jiadong back?

129
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:39,840
Chen Jiadong.

130
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:45,720
Twelve years ago,

131
00:05:47,200 --> 00:05:49,200
Chen Jiadong's father, Chen Xiyan,

132
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,320
killed my father.

133
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:55,130
This vengeance for my father's death,

134
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:56,120
I must take.

135
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:58,240
I

136
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:00,660
swear to tear Chen Jiadong

137
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:02,120
into pieces.

138
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:04,320
Furthermore,

139
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:08,360
whether it's Lin Zhongzheng

140
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:09,440
or Lin Mingshu,

141
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:10,840
that suspicious person,

142
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:13,370
they all have a certain influence.

143
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:15,440
Executing them

144
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,120
will definitely deal a severe blow

145
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:20,120
to the Chinese Chamber of Commerce.

146
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:21,720
It is a great opportunity for me

147
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:24,800
to completely crush them.

148
00:06:25,880 --> 00:06:26,960
It is enough to deter

149
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:28,400
all the Chinese throughout Malaya

150
00:06:28,400 --> 00:06:29,460
who are unfriendly

151
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:31,180
to the Great Japanese Empire.

152
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:31,960
Mr. Yamada.

153
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:34,400
The Chinese Chamber of Commerce

154
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:35,159
in Malaya

155
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:37,000
has deep roots.

156
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:39,240
They have a close relationship

157
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,570
with Director Songkan.

158
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:42,480
Eradicating them all at once

159
00:06:43,080 --> 00:06:44,040
won't be easy.

160
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:47,640
Songkan is extremely greedy for money.

161
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:50,960
He only helps the Chinese

162
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:52,600
to get their bribes.

163
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:54,600
This time,

164
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:57,120
I not only gave him gold,

165
00:06:57,960 --> 00:06:59,420
but also beautiful women.

166
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:02,320
He is indulging in pleasure

167
00:07:03,520 --> 00:07:05,400
and promised not to interfere

168
00:07:05,760 --> 00:07:07,560
in our dispute with the Chinese.

169
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:08,920
So,

170
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,320
go ahead and do it boldly.

171
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:21,980
Rest assured, Mr. Yamada.

172
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:22,900
I, Luo Wang,

173
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:25,000
will always be

174
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:27,100
to you and the Empire of Japan,

175
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:29,640
the most loyal hound.

176
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:31,360
Very well.

177
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:33,600
In three days,

178
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:35,580
you will be in charge of

179
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:38,140
escorting Lin Zhongzheng to the square.

180
00:07:38,840 --> 00:07:39,520
We will wait

181
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,530
for Chen Jiadong and his men

182
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,530
to walk right into our trap.

183
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:53,560
Mr. Qin.

184
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:54,100
Mr. Qin,

185
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:54,920
any news?

186
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:56,520
A Chinese brother

187
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:58,440
working in the police station prison

188
00:07:58,440 --> 00:07:59,360
just sent word.

189
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,620
He said in two days,

190
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:02,250
Luo Wang will escort Mr. Lin

191
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:04,020
from the prison to the square.

192
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:06,000
We only have two days.

193
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,720
Maybe we should hijack the prisoner.

194
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:08,850
Don't be impulsive.

195
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,320
It might end up getting you

196
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:11,400
and our Chamber of Commerce brothers

197
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:12,360
all killed.

198
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:13,080
No,

199
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:14,000
I'll go.

200
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:15,860
Yamada's target is me.

201
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,240
I'll rescue my dad first,

202
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:17,920
and then find a way

203
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:18,920
to deal with them.

204
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:19,690
Jiadong.

205
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:20,800
Don't forget.

206
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:21,840
Yamada's hatred for you

207
00:08:21,840 --> 00:08:23,160
isn't just because you took the evidence

208
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:24,490
and exposed his crimes.

209
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:26,120
He also resents your father

210
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:27,980
for killing his father back then.

211
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,440
Once you fall into his hands,

212
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:30,200
there's absolutely no way

213
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:31,260
he'll let you live.

214
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,929
If worse comes to worst,

215
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,090
I'll go beg Luo Wang.

216
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:34,919
No.

217
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,960
Nothing works!

218
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:37,960
You have no idea

219
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,820
how much Dad is suffering inside.

220
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:40,840
Wangshu.

221
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:46,280
Mr. Qin.

222
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:49,480
Is that Chinese police officer you mentioned

223
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,080
reliable?

224
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:51,640
There shouldn't be a problem.

225
00:08:51,640 --> 00:08:53,040
The Chamber of Commerce did him a favor.

226
00:08:53,040 --> 00:08:54,080
His name is Zheng Yi.

227
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:54,800
His family

228
00:08:55,040 --> 00:08:56,100
came from Quanzhou

229
00:08:56,160 --> 00:08:57,620
to Malaya to make a living.

230
00:08:57,760 --> 00:08:59,240
His father passed away last year.

231
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,120
All the funeral arrangements

232
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:02,380
were handled by our Chamber of Commerce.

233
00:09:04,560 --> 00:09:05,360
I have an idea.

234
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:07,080
It can save Dad

235
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:08,640
and cause Yamada and Luowang

236
00:09:08,640 --> 00:09:09,480
to have a rift,

237
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:10,360
leaving them no time

238
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,690
to press us constantly.

239
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:12,720
What idea?
